             was indicted for <rs id="t17960406-68-off377" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17960406-68-off377" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960406-68-off377" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17960406-68-cd378" type="crimeDate">22d of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960406-68-off377 t17960406-68-cd378"></join>, three pieces of printed dimity, containing eleven yards, value 27s. two pieces of jean, containing twenty yards, value 17s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17960406-68-victim746" type="victimName">
                           Matthew 
                           Parkinson
                        <interp inst="t17960406-68-victim746" type="surname" value="Parkinson"></interp>
